  		<p class="top-buffer-large">The best place to get a jump-start with Swift iOS development is the <a href="https://onemonth.com/courses/ios" target="_blank">One Month iOS tutorial</a> by Alfie Hanssen, lead mobile engineer at Vimeo. Along the way of 8 hours of video tutorial you will get familiar with the basics of Swift, get used to the development environment and create your very own clone of Instagram ready to submit to the app store.</p>
  	</div>
  	<div class="top-buffer-large">
  		<%= link_to "Check out One Month iOS now!", 'https://onemonth.com/courses/ios', class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block", target:"-blank" %>
    </div>
